demos.rationale:
```
@eggs{3}
@flour{125%g}
@milk{250%ml}
@sea salt{1%pinch}
@oil{}

Crack the @eggs{3} into a #blender{} then add the @flour{125%g}, @milk{250%ml} and @sea salt{1%pinch}, and blitz until smooth. Pour into a bowl and leave to stand for ~{15%minutes}. Melt the @oil{} in a large non-stick #frying pan{} on a medium heat, then tilt the pan so the @oil{} coats the surface. Pour in 1 ladle of batter and tilt again, so that the batter spreads all over the base, then cook for ~{1-2%minutes}, or until it starts to come away from the sides. Once golden underneath, flip the pancake over and cook for ~{1%minute}, or until cooked through. Serve straightaway with your favourite topping.
```

